## What Exists

### Shared Infrastructure (in share/util/)
- `shr_horiz_remap_mod.F90` — Type-bound CRS SpMV + source-gather MPI. 3-phase:
  read_mapfile → build_comm → apply. Reads ESMF weight files.
- `shr_vcoarsen_mod.F90` — Coordinate-agnostic overlap-weighted averaging
  (atmosphere pressure, ocean depth, land soil). Also: level selection,
  category sum/wgtavg for sea ice.
- `shr_derived_mod.F90` — Expression parser for "OUTPUT=A+B*2.0" syntax.
  Left-to-right evaluation with +,-,*,/ and numeric constants.

### EAM Wrappers (in components/eam/src/control/)
- `horiz_remap_mod.F90` — Per-tape remap via PIO with cam_grid registration
- `eam_vcoarsen.F90` — 3 modes: overlap avg, level select, pressure select
- `eam_derived.F90` — Chained expressions, tendencies, stage-aware phys/dyn split
- Integration: cam_history.F90, physpkg.F90, runtime_opts.F90, cam_comp.F90

### MPAS-Ocean (in components/mpas-ocean/src/)
Analysis members (analysis_members/):
- `mpas_ocn_fme_depth_coarsening.F` — Layer-thickness-weighted vertical averaging
  onto configurable depth levels. Generic field dispatch from namelist.
  Uses shr_vcoarsen_avg per cell.
- `mpas_ocn_fme_derived_fields.F` — SST, SSS, combined surface heat flux.
  When horiz_remap_file set, remaps to lat-lon via PIO.
- `mpas_ocn_fme_vertical_reduce.F` — Column-integrated OHC, FWC, KE plus
  5 generic slots (vertReduceField01..05) for user-configured reductions.
Shared (shared/):
- `mpas_ocn_fme_horiz_remap.F` — Wraps shr_horiz_remap_t for MPAS cell
  decomposition. PIO output to (lon, lat, Time) NetCDF files.

### MPAS-Sea-Ice (in components/mpas-seaice/src/)
- `mpas_seaice_fme_derived_fields.F` — Category aggregation (ice area/volume/snow
  totals, area-weighted means) + air stress rotation via
  seaice_latlon_vector_rotation_backward. Horiz remap integration.
- `mpas_seaice_fme_horiz_remap.F` — Same PIO pattern as MPAS-O.

### ELM (in components/elm/src/main/)
- `elm_fme_derived.F90` — Scans histFileMod masterlist for fields by name,
  evaluates shr_derived_eval. Registered with hist_addfld1d (gridcell-level).
- `elm_fme_vcoarsen.F90` — Maps TSOI→col_es%t_soisno, H2OSOI→col_ws%h2osoi_vol,
  SOILICE→col_ws%h2osoi_ice. Calls shr_vcoarsen_avg with zisoi coordinates.
  Registered with hist_addfld1d (column-level).
- Integration: controlMod (readnl), elm_initializeMod (register before
  hist_htapes_build), elm_driver (update before hist_update_hbuf).

### MOSART (in components/mosart/src/riverroute/)
- `RtmFmeDerived.F90` — Maps field names to rtmCTL members (QSUR_LIQ,
  QSUB_LIQ, VOLR_LIQ, etc.). Registered with RtmHistAddfld.
- Integration: RtmMod (readnl, register after RtmHistFldsInit, update
  before RtmHistUpdateHbuf).

